>Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Varying industries and a wide range of products</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Focus on practical problems, not on values, economics, or logistics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Organize all steps of the production on a blueprint</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Factories grow as you unlock more desk space</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully simulated Day/Night-cycle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take care of your workers! Work them too hard and they drop like flies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute model-town art-style</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Razer Chroma support</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/574720/extras/563e6579f9ec9f34336476397c9e4b01.avif?t=1770373859\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p>",
